Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}聖天空戰記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要墜入愛河每個人都會變得如此孤單?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正擁抱著比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切必定都是為了讓我倆能綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用淚水來呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你早就給了我 最寶貴的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野學長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.85,0:01:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是再多躺一下子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是夢嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:01:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說我回來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好渴喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們繞去哪家店坐坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉,要不要一起去暍茶?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還得整理記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等小瞳一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別去當電燈泡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,那樣不行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是要當電燈泡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞心眼的由加莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧\N拜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見了,由加莉\N先走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋亞行星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到月亮與地球\N同時在天上出現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是個浪漫主義者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會作那樣的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的墜子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我祖母的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它很有趣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要像這樣子擺動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就會像鐘擺一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一秒一次地,一直擺動下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曉得…接下來會發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長會擺動起墜子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 3 4 56
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:04:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7 8 9 10
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 1 12 13 14…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野學長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉,我在叫你耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也說句話嘛,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕月堂的草莓麻繕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑠倉屋的起司蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湘南本鋪的銅鑼燒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義大利傳統店的薄荷冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上每天奉上不同的點心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就放過你這次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟那天…那個命運之日的前一天一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜她曾說過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湘南小館的肉丁洋蔥燴飯超級好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的臉色很不好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經知道了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有算過你跟學長的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是算出來的結果不好的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉,你是怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:05:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要是喜歡的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要是喜歡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是早點表白吧\N由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,我不小心聽到學長他們的聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說天野學長可能會去國外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他父親的工作所以得到英國去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.93,0:06:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能連縣大會都沒辦法參加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我最要好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很明白你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是早點表白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不說一定會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你那麼喜歡天野學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳消失了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是叫人模不著頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是被寨巴哈抓走了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是靠多倫卡喀的科學力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:08:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能製造出光柱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小瞳是到哪去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很想回幻之月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣對我們來說不是正好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來,寨巴哈也無法敔動命運改變裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈…寨巴哈軍在國境布下了重兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探測不到少女的反應,多倫卡喀大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不確定因素
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何我的夢想就是無法實現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,洗澡水放好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你一直…一直都喜歡學長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來以為自己對學長是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來打算要守護她…守護小瞳一輩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她卻離去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我的心境為何會如此平靜?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的離去確實讓我感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我同樣為她能回到,自己的世界感到高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是因為她很像妹妹很像謝蕾娜的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這張牌會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要回去那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想再回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:12:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人,您是怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您很在意小瞳的事,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰在意她了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您編人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都待在您身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以對您再清楚不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.02,0:13:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您很在意小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您喜歡小瞳,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人,看來您還沒察覺到\N自己的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家從好久以前就曉得了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳不也總是那麼說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"意念一定能傳達得到"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.78,0:13:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以您的意念一定會傳達得到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能傳達給小瞳知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的是謝蕾娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然十年不見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我絕不會錯認自己的妹妹,謝蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得她至今都流落何方,真是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還失去了記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了記憶?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我外出征戰的這段時間家妹就勞煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是天空騎士的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我在皇宮照顧她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧,謝蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝蕾娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是什麼地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裏做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是幻人?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈久卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈久卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈久卡!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:15:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈久卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先別走,迪蘭度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾,我並不清楚他的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但能確定的是,他的背後似乎有魔導士在操控
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔導士?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接聽命於多倫卡喀的寨巴哈的科學家們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾聽說他們為了改變\N人的命運而進行人體實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把捉來的小孩子們…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人體實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝蕾娜她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝蕾娜竟然是被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都已經知道牛頓是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到蘋果從樹上掉落\N才發現萬有引力的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過其實牛頓還對煉金術及魔法多有涉獵…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在呼喚著我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多倫卡喀大人,已經準備就緒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要讓龍與少女的引力昇華
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就能夠產生命運素粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對,引力仍存在著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女一定會再度現身於蓋亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點的話,天野學長就要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我沒能注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是最好的朋友卻沒能注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想見他,我想再見他一面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運素粒子達臨界點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝置敔動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,我要再見你一次面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎,你準備好了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7  8…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,我不會再讓你離開我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是蓋亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到了蓋亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個紛爭的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:23:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手吧,弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.80,0:23:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對幸運圈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:57.54,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月兒彼方藍色探照燈照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:05.99,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降臨的天使 你究竟是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:13.62,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的門扉即將開啟　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:19.77,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不放過這令人興奮的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:22.13,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.37,0:22:27.14,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃燒般的神秘雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:30.98,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真無邪的笑容讓我傾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.05,0:22:34.78,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深處的暗示只傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.85,0:22:38.79,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了無止盡的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:42.29,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心的鼓動無法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:49.76,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想帶著你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:57.53,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:05.98,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:13.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:19.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.83,0:22:22.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.37,0:22:27.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:30.97,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:34.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.85,0:22:38.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:42.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:49.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい

